1. *Crvena* ruža je simbol ljubavi. (A red rose is a symbol of love.)
2. Njen omiljeni boja je *crvena*. (Her favourite colour is red.)
3. *Crveni* ružičasti cvetovi su se pojavili u vrtu. (The red pink flowers appeared in the garden.)
4. Na ceo dan se okupio *crven* oblak. (A red cloud gathered for the whole day.)
5. Ona je nosila *crvenu* haljinu. (She was wearing a red dress.)